cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use gatekept, please cite it."
title: gatekept
abstract: >-
  A macOS security audit and optimization CLI that catches fake, cracked, and
  tampered applications that signature antivirus misses, using Apple's codesign
  and spctl. Audits hardening posture, persistence (LaunchAgents/Daemons,
  Login Items/BTM, cron, shell configs), and /tmp staging used by AMOS and
  ClickFix. Also packaged as a Claude Code and OpenAI Codex skill.
type: software
authors:
  - name: "myusufyilmaz"
repository-code: "https://github.com/myusufyilmaz/gatekept"
url: "https://github.com/myusufyilmaz/gatekept"
license: MIT
version: "1.3.1"
keywords:
  - macOS
  - security
  - security-audit
  - malware-detection
  - codesign
  - gatekeeper
  - AMOS
  - ClickFix
